---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Industries | Foremost Machine, Inc.">
  <section class="section-shell">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">Industries We Support</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-300">Foremost Machine, Inc. partners with commercial organizations requiring reliable machined components and stable production communication.</p>
    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="card"><h2 class="text-xl text-white">Industrial Equipment</h2><p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Component supply for OEM and MRO programs with repeat demand.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h2 class="text-xl text-white">Automation & Robotics</h2><p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Precision parts for high-cycle assemblies, fixtures, and tooling.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h2 class="text-xl text-white">Energy & Infrastructure</h2><p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Durable components with documentation and revision control needs.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h2 class="text-xl text-white">Transportation</h2><p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Support for brackets, housings, and mechanical system subcomponents.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h2 class="text-xl text-white">Medical Device Manufacturing</h2><p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Commercial-grade production support for non-consumer components.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h2 class="text-xl text-white">General B2B Manufacturing</h2><p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Low-to-mid volume recurring orders with quality control checkpoints.</p></article>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href="/request-access" class="rounded-md bg-brand-500 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-brand-700">Request Access</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="rounded-md border border-slate-600 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-100 hover:border-slate-400">Talk to Sales</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
